data.description:
Welcome to this beautiful and move-in ready home located in the fantastic neighborhood of Sage Creek. 

This spacious residence boasts a modern and inviting open floor concept, perfect for today's lifestyle. With three generously sized bedrooms upstairs, you will have plenty of space for your family or guests. Upstairs, you will also find two well-appointed bathrooms, and a loft area, ensuring convenience and comfort.

The living areas downstairs are designed with a contemporary open floor plan, creating a seamless flow between the living room, dining area, and kitchen. Kitchen features: granite countertops, island, all white cabinets, and generous size pantry.  This layout is perfect for entertaining friends and family.

One of the standout features of this property is the large backyard with recently installed Zoysia sod. The backyard comes completely fenced providing privacy and security for outdoor activities and relaxation. Whether you are enjoying a BBQ with friends or letting your pets roam freely, this yard is a true asset.

 With an additional driveway you'll have plenty of room for parking and/or storage.

This home is better than new, meticulously maintained, and move-in ready. It combines modern amenities with the comfort of a well-stablished neighborhood. Don't miss the opportunity to make this wonderful house your new home!
